{"tid":1782241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國球星奧斯爾呼籲關注維吾爾人 中國網民鬧爆兼燒波衫","createTime":"2019-12-13T19:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T11:05:40.000Z","uid":92301,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d66d4c641e4441f0386df64adde685aff75b06c1","tid":1782241,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"周五德國球星奧斯爾在Twitter上載兩張圖片，不滿中國打壓新疆維吾爾人，此文一出內地網民反應極大，更有人在圖片下貼上火燒奧斯爾球衣的影片。<br />\n<br />\n去年奧斯爾就曾因與土耳其總統合照惹來風波，更因感受到針對而退出德國國家隊。即使如此，奧斯爾仍然在Twitter上發表文章支持維吾爾族人，內容大概為不滿中國將穆斯林關入集中營，婦女被逼嫁給中國人，同時對於穆斯林人對此一無所知而感到無奈，當中引用了一句：「想要停止迫害，就要讓其公開。」<br />\n<br />\n奧斯爾的言論一出，隨即惹來中國網民的不滿，更認為這位德國球星是正在侵犯中國主權，干涉他國內政。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191214/HIQMPKWIDYQU7XMILOYIQRIAL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191214%2FHIQMPKWIDYQU7XMILOYIQRIAL4%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=fe35769a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191214%2FHIQMPKWIDYQU7XMILOYIQRIAL4%2F&h=f4bdefd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191214/HIQMPKWIDYQU7XMILOYIQRIAL4/</a>"},{"pid":"ed6bd4d0e2774de3b2a2ec2741e3c7ddea97b388","tid":1782241,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T19:24:50.000Z","msg":"諗起NBA罷睇就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2855bd3a5dc2d85e319068a31ec14df88d48d2f5","tid":1782241,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T01:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c4fdef187d4004706727157a5794b1ea0130436","tid":1782241,"uid":172826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際戰線着緊火 1222 1530愛丁堡見<br />\n<br />\n「行動」突發 12月22號有「支持維吾爾人集會」無人知！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782177\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論